features: GHOSTFACE KILLAH SUPER7 ACTION FIGURE: Hip-hop legend and Wu-Tang Clan founding member Ghostface Killah joins the Super7 action toy figures lineup
CONCERT-READY ACCESSORIES: This action figure comes with gold chains and microphone accessories, allowing you to immortalize iconic songs by the legendary hip hop artist
3.75-INCH ACTION FIGURE: Ghostface Killah figure is 3.75" tall with the rest of the Super7 hip hop ReAction figures lineup

PREMIUM ACTION FIGURES: Relive the good times all over again with our ReAction figures, classic 3.75" scale action figure toys that fit in the palm of your hand; Featuring Mighty Morphin Power Rangers, G.I. Joe, Toho, Who Framed Roger Rabbit, and more

COLLECTIBLE TOYS & FIGURES: From TMNT action figures and G.I. Joe skateboard decks to Power Rangers t-shirts and SpongeBob toys, Super7 makes the perfect retro collectibles, vintage toys, and nostalgia gifts for pop culture fanatics and collectors
body.description: A founding member of Wu-Tang Clan, Ghostface Killah has also carved out a name for himself as a solo artist known for his fast-paced flow and elaborate story-telling skills! This 3.75” scale, articulated Ghostface Killah ReAction figure is inspired by the cover art of his debut solo album “Ironman” and includes microphone and gold chain action figure accessories. The ReAction figure of Ghostface Killah will make a killer addition to any Wu-Tang Clan or hip-hop icons collection! Super7 makes retro collectibles, vintage toys, and nostalgia gifts for pop culture fanatics and collectors. We grew up with giant monsters, comic books, punk, science fiction, skateboarding, robots, and rebellion. No one made what we wanted. So we made it ourselves.
